🏗️ Create Database

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

💻 Example

```python id="create_database"
import mysql.connector

connection = mysql.connector.connect(
    host="localhost",
    user="root",
    password="password"
)

cursor = connection.cursor()

cursor.execute(
    "CREATE DATABASE company"
)
```

---

📋 Show Databases

---

💻 Example

```python id="show_databases"
cursor.execute(
    "SHOW DATABASES"
)

for db in cursor:
    print(db)
```

---

▶️ Sample Output

```text id="show_db_output"
company
mysql
information_schema
```

