🛡️ Exception Handling

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

💻 Example

```python id="db_exception"
import mysql.connector

try:

    connection = mysql.connector.connect(
        host="localhost",
        user="root",
        password="password"
    )

    print("Connected")

except mysql.connector.Error as err:

    print(
        "Error:",
        err
    )
```

---

🔐 SQL Injection Prevention

Always use parameterized queries.

---

❌ Unsafe

```python id="unsafe_query"
query = f"""
SELECT * FROM users
WHERE name = '{user}'
"""
```

---

✅ Safe

```python id="safe_query"
query = """
SELECT * FROM users
WHERE name = %s
"""

cursor.execute(
    query,
    (user,)
)
```

